# Etch-a-Sketch Project

This project showcases my current skills in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features

- Dynamic grid system
- Interactive drawing experience using mouse hover
- Built using Flexbox for layout

## What I Learned

- DOM manipulation with JavaScript
- Dynamically creating and styling elements
- Using Flexbox for grid layouts
- Handling user interaction events

## How It Works

- The grid is generated entirely through JavaScript
- Users can adjust grid size, clear grid, and switch between modes of coloring.
- Each square responds to hover, simulating drawing
